transformations.description: This source is a custom query using a union. The first portion of the query will use the basicpolicy_stg, claimstats_stg, policystats_stg, risk_stg,  and line_stg tables. The second portion of the query will use the basicpolicyapp_stg, risk_application_stg, and line_stg tables.
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT 
bp.systemid as policy_system_id,
bp.cmmcontainer as policy_cmm_container,
bp.id as policy_reference_id,
bp.shellpolicyind,
bp.carriercd as policy_carriercd,
cs.carriercd as claimstat_carriercd,
ps.carriercd as policystat_carriercd,
bp.policynumber,
bp.policyversion,
r.systemid as risk_system_id,
r.id as risk_reference_id,
l.systemid as line_system_id,
l.id as line_reference_id,
l.linecd,
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_id,
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_md5_hash_value 
FROM dbo.risk_stg r
LEFT JOIN dbo.basicpolicy_stg bp
ON r.systemid = bp.systemid
AND r.cmmcontainer = bp.cmmcontainer
LEFT JOIN 
(select 
policyref, 
carriercd,
rank() over (partition by policyref order by statsequence desc) as rnk
from dbo.claimstats_stg) cs 
ON bp.systemid = cs.policyref
and cs.rnk = 1
LEFT JOIN 
(select 
policyref, 
carriercd,
rank() over (partition by policyref order by statsequence desc) as rnk
from dbo.policystats_stg) ps
ON ps.policyref = bp.systemid
and ps.rnk = 1
LEFT JOIN dbo.line_stg l
ON bp.systemid = l.systemid
AND bp.cmmcontainer = l.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr 
on prkr.policy_system_id = bp.systemid 
and prkr.policy_reference_id = bp.id 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = bp.cmmcontainer 
and prkr.risk_system_id = r.systemid 
and prkr.risk_id = r.id
and prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
UNION
SELECT distinct
bp.systemid as policy_system_id,
bp.cmmcontainer as policy_cmm_container,
bp.id as policy_reference_id,
bp.shellpolicyind,
bp.carriercd as policy_carriercd,
null as claimstat_carriercd,
null as policystat_carriercd,
bp.policynumber,
bp.policyversion,
r.risk_application_system_id as risk_system_id,
r.risk_application_id as risk_reference_id,
l.systemid as line_system_id,
l.id as line_reference_id,
l.linecd,
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_id,
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_md5_hash_value 
FROM dbo.risk_application_stg r
LEFT JOIN dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg bp
ON r.risk_application_system_id = bp.systemid
AND r.risk_application_cmm_container = bp.cmmcontainer
LEFT JOIN dbo.line_stg l
ON bp.systemid = l.systemid
AND bp.cmmcontainer = l.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr 
on prkr.policy_system_id = bp.systemid 
and prkr.policy_reference_id = bp.id 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = bp.cmmcontainer 
and prkr.risk_system_id = r.risk_application_system_id
and prkr.risk_id = r.risk_application_id
and prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

transformations.description: This expression will implement logic for the following fields - policy_company, policy_number, policy_module_number, policy_key, and policy_key_code. We will also create the hash key value for comparing data to the target.
transformations.name: exp_set_policy_details

fields.description: This will select which carriercd field to use for later logic
fields.name: v_carriercd
fields.expression:
IIF(shellpolicyind = 'true' and NOT ISNULL(claimstat_carriercd), claimstat_carriercd,
IIF((policy_carriercd = 'ADVR' or ISNULL(policy_carriercd)) and NOT ISNULL(policystat_carriercd), policystat_carriercd, policy_carriercd))

fields.description: This will convert the carriercd to a text-readable version
fields.name: v_carriercd_decode

fields.description: This will convert the policy number if it is for a shell policy
fields.name: v_policy_number
fields.expression: IIF(shellpolicyind = 'true', IIF(linecd = 'Homeowners', CONCAT('HP1', policynumber), IIF( linecd = 'Dwelling', CONCAT('FP2', policynumber), CONCAT('SBP3', policynumber) ) ), policynumber )

fields.description: This will format the policy version to be zero-padded
fields.name: v_policy_module_number
policy_key
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(v_policy_number) OR ISNULL(v_policy_module_number), NULL,
v_policy_number || v_policy_module_number)

fields.name: policy_key_code
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(v_carriercd_decode) OR ISNULL(v_policy_number) OR ISNULL(v_policy_module_number) OR ISNULL(risk_reference_id), NULL, 
v_carriercd_decode || v_policy_number || v_policy_module_number || risk_reference_id)

fields.name: md5_hash_value
fields.expression: MD5('policy_system_id' || to_char(policy_system_id) || 'policy_cmm_container' || policy_cmm_container || 'policy_reference_id' || policy_reference_id || 'shellpolicyind' || shellpolicyind || 'policynumber' || policynumber || 'policyversion' || policyversion || 'risk_system_id' || to_char(risk_system_id) || 'risk_reference_id' || risk_reference_id || 'line_system_id' || to_char(line_system_id) || 'line_reference_id' || line_reference_id || 'linecd' || linecd || 'policy_company' || v_carriercd_decode)
